When you're in a boardroom,

00:18:43.200 --> 00:18:44.940
especially when you've
been like the founder

00:18:44.940 --> 00:18:48.360
and face of a company for 15
years, you're in a boardroom

00:18:48.360 --> 00:18:50.970
with four other people

00:18:50.970 --> 00:18:55.500
and they're all telling you
why the watch people die.

00:18:55.500 --> 00:18:58.320
community is an important part of Reddit

00:18:58.320 --> 00:19:01.080
