Like, am I wrong on this?

00:19:16.260 --> 00:19:20.070
'cause like I know this community
is full of snuff videos,

00:19:20.070 --> 00:19:22.230
suicide videos, murder videos, mostly

00:19:22.230 --> 00:19:23.670
of people in the developing world.

00:19:23.670 --> 00:19:26.145
'cause that's how that video
footage gets leaked out.

00:19:26.145 --> 00:19:29.190
And there are millions of people
on Reddit who come to this

00:19:29.190 --> 00:19:31.920
and discuss it and share and bond

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:35.160
and like, that feels vile.

00:19:35.160 --> 00:19:37.710
That feels wrong. It's not
something I'm proud of.

00:19:37.710 --> 00:19:40.715
But when you're told, you know,

00:19:40.715 --> 00:19:44.040
and the the room is very
obviously against you and

00:19:44.040 --> 00:19:45.000
and told, no, no, no,

00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:47.310
it's, don't worry about it, you're wrong.

00:19:48.450 --> 00:19:52.830
It was, it was a weird,
very surreal experience.

