Serena clocked it real quick.

00:19:54.060 --> 00:19:55.470
She was like, no, those people are crazy.

00:19:55.470 --> 00:19:57.210
Watch people die is a horrible community.

00:19:57.210 --> 00:19:58.470
And you were absolutely right.

00:19:58.470 --> 00:20:01.560
And thank God I had one person in my life

00:20:01.560 --> 00:20:03.840
